    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:31,985" end="00:00:50,359">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:50,359" end="00:00:52,756">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Woman] I think it is impossible to overestimate</span></p>
      <p begin="00:00:52,756" end="00:00:55,048">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the importance of Vidal Sassoon.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:55,048" end="00:00:56,186">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Man] He's probably one of the greatest,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:00:56,186" end="00:00:59,853">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">if not the greatest hairdresserthat's ever lived.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:59,853" end="00:01:04,909">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] With raw talent and drive and ambition and just sheer guts</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:04,909" end="00:01:07,526">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I will not give up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:07,526" end="00:01:11,081">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He built something that rocked the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:11,081" end="00:01:14,174">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] It was one man with an amazing innovative idea</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:14,174" end="00:01:16,025">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that has stood the test of time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:16,025" end="00:01:17,702">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic"> [Host] Our next guest became famous</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:17,702" end="00:01:20,286">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for creating The Shape, The Five-point, The Bob,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:20,286" end="00:01:21,951">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the many, many more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:21,951" end="00:01:24,527">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- They were the styles which set him off</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:24,527" end="00:01:30,445">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">on the path to creating a multimilliondollar international corporation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:30,445" end="00:01:33,285">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Man] Well, he's an international celebrity really who revolutionized</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:33,285" end="00:01:35,762">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the way women of the worldlooked on the outside</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:35,762" end="00:01:38,195">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and how they view themselves on the inside.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:38,195" end="00:01:40,460">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] Vidal was completely established</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:40,460" end="00:01:44,282">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">as the leading personin hair in the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:44,282" end="00:01:48,659">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] Probably the biggest legacy in modern hairdressing</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:48,659" end="00:01:50,217">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is the name Vidal Sassoon.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:50,217" end="00:01:53,196">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] He's like, I supposed, like a big deal in hairdressing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:53,196" end="00:01:54,953">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Woman] I think if you went to Japanand asked them [chuckles]</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:54,953" end="00:01:56,391">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">what hairdressers do you know?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:56,391" end="00:01:59,002"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They would say,</span> "Vidal Sassoon." <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They would know the name.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:59,002" end="00:02:01,558">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] It's like being a boxerin the time of Muhammad Ali</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:01,558" end="00:02:05,662">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">or being a physicist and working next to Einstein</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:05,662" end="00:02:07,483">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because he was that good.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:07,483" end="00:02:10,644">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] We think of Sassoon, we also think liberation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:10,644" end="00:02:13,737">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] He just seems to exudethis magic around him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:13,737" end="00:02:16,302">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] If I was the Queen of England, I would knight him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:16,302" end="00:02:18,743">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] So much of Sassoon is a myth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:18,743" end="00:02:23,287"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] I fought some great people in my time,but for me, he is</span> the person.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:23,287" end="00:02:25,120">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Yeah, he is the Messiah.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:25,120" end="00:02:30,236">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Vidal Sassoon] If you don't look good,we don't look good.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:30,236" end="00:03:12,076">&#9834; [rock music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:24,600" end="00:03:32,490">-[Vidal Sassoon] You know I'm sitting here<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>reflecting really at 81.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32,490" end="00:03:35,614">Who would've dreamt that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>sixty seven years ago,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35,614" end="00:03:42,717">at the age of fourteen, there I was <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the East End of London.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:42,717" end="00:03:44,201">A "shampoo boy."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:44,201" end="00:03:49,585">And then sitting here, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>over sixty years later.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:49,585" end="00:03:53,439">And I'm wondering, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>"How did it all happen?"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:53,439" end="00:03:56,202">How did so much adventure happen?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56,202" end="00:04:01,067">&#9834; [music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01,067" end="00:04:03,735">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> [Vidal Sassoon] Go back all those years, you think</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:03,735" end="00:04:08,485">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the excitement, the creativity,the people you've met.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:08,485" end="00:04:26,257">[people chatting]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:26,257" end="00:04:29,096">- [Michael Gordon] So we're gonna go ahead<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and start assembling the wall</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29,096" end="00:04:30,890">because Vidal is coming to see it.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:30,890" end="00:04:33,264">I've known Vidal about fifteen years</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33,264" end="00:04:35,163">and I consider him a really good friend.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35,163" end="00:04:38,777">I've always been in the position when<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I was the elder talking to other people.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38,777" end="00:04:40,867">So, having someone <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>who you respect immensely</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40,867" end="00:04:44,502">and who has such an impact <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>on people's lives as a friend.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44,502" end="00:04:46,653">It's rather wonderful.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46,653" end="00:04:49,202">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The more I got to know him,I realized we had lot in common.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:49,202" end="00:04:52,674">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We were both hairdressers.</span>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That's how we started off in London.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:52,674" end="00:04:55,907">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Both transitioned into having product companies.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:55,907" end="00:04:58,434">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I realized that, actually,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:58,434" end="00:05:01,434">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">nobody had really recorded his achievements, his life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:01,434" end="00:05:06,049">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So, I thought a bookwas absolutely necessary.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:06,049" end="00:05:08,228">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> I felt like it was reallyimportant to capture.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:08,228" end="00:05:11,589">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had an impact on the world that no hairdresser has ever had.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:11,589" end="00:05:13,339">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He changed the way women looked.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13,339" end="00:05:16,714">&#9834; [music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16,714" end="00:05:19,710">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This was the way books used to be produced to magazines.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:19,710" end="00:05:21,688">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You put them on the floor or the wall.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:21,688" end="00:05:23,969">You did a layout.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23,969" end="00:05:27,546">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I think he'll really be moved to see this.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:27,546" end="00:05:31,291">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There were series of three4-hour interviews.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:31,291" end="00:05:33,125">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Different places, different times.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:33,125" end="00:05:37,399">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The first place we interviewed himwas in his house in Beverly Hills.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:37,399" end="00:05:49,441">[birds chirping] [water gushing]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49,441" end="00:05:53,729">- So, you were born 1928, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in Shepherds Bush?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:53,729" end="00:05:57,017">- When I was, maybe, 2 1/2 to 3 ,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57,017" end="00:05:58,868">my mother was evicted.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58,868" end="00:06:03,549">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You have to remember, it was 1928 I was born.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:03,549" end="00:06:08,931">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So in '30, '31, the Depression was on.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:08,931" end="00:06:12,086">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father left us. Had a young brother.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:12,086" end="00:06:15,004">And unlike today, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>where we're multi-cultural,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15,014" end="00:06:17,484">being Jewish, we stood out in those days.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17,484" end="00:06:20,638">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We needed somewhere to live.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:20,638" end="00:06:25,826">So, she appealed to the Jewish authorities<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to take us into this orphanage here.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25,826" end="00:06:31,106">And I spent from five to eleven<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the orphanage,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31,106" end="00:06:34,849">and sang in the synagogue choir.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34,849" end="00:06:53,465">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:53,465" end="00:06:58,092">Hmmm</p>
      <p begin="00:06:58,092" end="00:07:03,711">Seventy two years ago, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>this is where I used to sit.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03,711" end="00:07:05,786">I was a choir boy.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05,786" end="00:07:11,596">The choir master, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>he'd rap my knuckles on occasion.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11,596" end="00:07:13,507">[laughs]</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13,507" end="00:07:16,998">'Cause, you know, we were kids<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and we were naughty at times.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16,998" end="00:07:21,015">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But they were charming services.they were very warm, very gentle.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:21,461" end="00:07:25,497">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Right now, at this moment,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:25,497" end="00:07:28,241">I don't know if I did then &#8211; <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I was far too young.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:28,241" end="00:07:31,463">But right now, I'm feeling all spiritual.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:31,463" end="00:07:38,840">There's a sense of peace here <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and it's a wonderful-shaped synagogue.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38,840" end="00:07:43,751">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It hasn't changed. I can't think of anything that's changed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:43,751" end="00:07:48,110">To give you just a few bars<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of something that we used to sing,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:48,110" end="00:07:50,265">we used to go <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hallelujah, Hallelujah.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:07:50,265" end="00:07:53,585">And the tune was<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>&#9834; [Hallelujah] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:53,585" end="00:07:55,728">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">&#9834; [Hallelujah] &#9834; </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:55,728" end="00:08:08,647">[singing continues]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:08,647" end="00:08:10,601">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What I miss most is my mom.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10,601" end="00:08:17,957">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They only allowed me to see heronce a month.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:17,957" end="00:08:20,979">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I ran away from the orphanage.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:20,979" end="00:08:25,381">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Went to my dad which is so much closerthan the East End where my mother lived.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:25,381" end="00:08:30,142">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He got me back to the orphanageas quick as he could.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:30,142" end="00:08:33,861">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I could see that there was no caring or love.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:33,861" end="00:08:39,741">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> You could tell that as he walked away,when he passed me over to the authorities,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:39,741" end="00:08:42,659">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that he already had something else on his mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:42,659" end="00:08:45,330">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He didn't even look at me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:45,330" end="00:08:52,534">And I think that moment, was when I lost <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>any love that I had for him.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:52,534" end="00:08:55,314">Never saw him again.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:55,945" end="00:08:59,089">- [Betty Sassoon] You see, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I had two beautiful sons.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:59,089" end="00:09:00,734">And I'd always had that feeling</p>
      <p begin="00:09:00,734" end="00:09:05,987">that I wanted my sons to grow up<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to be very proud of their mother.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:05,987" end="00:09:08,415">And think that helped me an awful lot.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:08,415" end="00:09:12,657">- If there's anything you'd wish for me<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the future, what would it be?</p>
      <p begin="00:09:12,657" end="00:09:14,457">- Oh, God, and this is the truth...</p>
      <p begin="00:09:14,457" end="00:09:19,299">I wish happiness in your life<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>because you deserve it, son.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:19,299" end="00:09:21,967">If anybody deserves it,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that's you because you've been&#8230;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:21,967" end="00:09:24,010">to me...</p>
      <p begin="00:09:24,010" end="00:09:27,559">Please, It&#8217;s the truth the best son <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>a mother could ever have.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:27,559" end="00:09:34,672">And I think I am blessed by God<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to have such a son.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:34,672" end="00:09:36,727">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Vidal] Her life was a painful one.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:36,727" end="00:09:40,618">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Mine was different. I knew nothing else.The orphanage and then the war broke out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:40,618" end="00:09:45,086">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Churchill] We can go on to the end.We can fight in France.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:45,086" end="00:09:47,132">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We can fight on the seas and oceans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:47,132" end="00:09:49,235">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] And then suddenly, we were all picked-up.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:09:49,235" end="00:09:52,978">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All the kids of London and sent to the country.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:52,978" end="00:09:55,983">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Where we lived with cows and sheep for the next few years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55,983" end="00:09:58,041">And of course very nice people <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that took us in.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:58,041" end="00:10:01,628">I came back to London at fourteen<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and the war was still on.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01,628" end="00:10:05,563">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And we were sleeping down the shelteras everybody did.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:05,563" end="00:10:10,167">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And the Luftwaffe was rearrangingthe streets of London every night.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:10,167" end="00:10:12,416">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The architecture was changing at every moment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:12,416" end="00:10:15,878">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Churchill] We shall defend our islandwhatever the cost may be.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10:15,878" end="00:10:18,199">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] I had a job as a glove cutter.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10:18,199" end="00:10:20,008">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was cutting the little snippets</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:20,008" end="00:10:23,186">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that they would sew the glovestogether with.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:23,186" end="00:10:24,884">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It seemed I always had a pair of shears in my hand.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:24,884" end="00:10:27,522">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Except for three months in London.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:27,522" end="00:10:31,381">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They needed messenger boys who had bikes</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:31,381" end="00:10:35,729">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to take messages fromthe city to the darks.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:35,729" end="00:10:39,898">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mother had remarried Nathan G., Nathan Goldberg.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:39,898" end="00:10:43,809">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Great guy. He got me a bike and I got the job.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:43,809" end="00:10:45,058">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The job was fascinating</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:45,058" end="00:10:48,877">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because the streets were blockedand buildings were down.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:48,877" end="00:10:53,360">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I was riding this bike at fourteen, really having fun.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:53,360" end="00:10:54,377">[explosions]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:54,377" end="00:10:56,643">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You know you began to feellike a war hero.</span>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[chuckles]</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:56,643" end="00:10:58,151">[crowd cheering]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:58,151" end="00:11:01,205">- [Churchill] ...and in the streets, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we'll fight in the hills.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:01,205" end="00:11:03,686">We shall never surrender.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:03,686" end="00:11:08,047">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mother, she was always concerned,saying, "You gotta learn a trade!"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:08,047" end="00:11:11,124">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">She said, "Well, I've had a premonition."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:11,124" end="00:11:11,995">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"What's that mother?"</span>
