      <p begin="00:11:11,995" end="00:11:14,574">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">She said, "You're going to be a hairdresser."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:14,574" end="00:11:16,489">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I said,[whispers] "I'm going to be what?"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:16,489" end="00:11:18,957">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">She said, "A hairdresser."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:18,957" end="00:11:21,463">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So she walked me by the hand.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:21,463" end="00:11:24,410">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Into a man called Adolph Cohen,in White Chapel Road.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:24,410" end="00:11:26,513">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> Now, White Chapel is the heart of the ghetto.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:26,513" end="00:11:28,050">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And there was this wonderfullittle man.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:28,050" end="00:11:30,013">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He couldn't have been more than five feet.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:30,013" end="00:11:32,720">He asked for a hundred guinnes.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:32,720" end="00:11:38,118">Now that was a a hundred pounds <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and a hundred shillings in those days.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:38,118" end="00:11:40,768">Which is an impossible figure.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:40,768" end="00:11:43,511">My mother said, "We don't have <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>a hundred buttons."</p>
      <p begin="00:11:43,511" end="00:11:49,200">I was kinda smiling because I was relieved<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I wasn't going to be a hairdresser.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:49,200" end="00:11:51,946">So I went to the door <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and opened it for my mother</p>
      <p begin="00:11:51,946" end="00:11:53,557">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and ushered her through.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:53,557" end="00:11:55,944">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I doffed the cap.He followed us out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:55,944" end="00:11:58,832">He said "You seem to have rather <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>good manners, young man."</p>
      <p begin="00:11:58,832" end="00:12:03,948">"Start Monday." He looked at my mom <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and said, "Let's forget the fee."</p>
      <p begin="00:12:03,948" end="00:12:06,317">So my apprenticeship cost nothing.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:06,317" end="00:12:14,434">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:12:14,434" end="00:12:17,436">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was apprentice for two years with Adolph.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:17,436" end="00:12:19,401">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Extraordinary man.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:19,401" end="00:12:23,412">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Pressed trousers every morning.Clean nails. Clean Shoes.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:23,412" end="00:12:26,277">Middle of a war --<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>how was that possible?</p>
      <p begin="00:12:26,277" end="00:12:27,959">He was a disciplinarian!</p>
      <p begin="00:12:27,959" end="00:12:34,267">And i think that had<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>an enormous effect on my sense of how</p>
      <p begin="00:12:34,267" end="00:12:37,698">we should progress in our craft.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:37,698" end="00:12:42,458">- [Joshua Calvin] They can't help even at <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>80 years of age to be mesmerized by him.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:42,458" end="00:12:44,594">And he's such a well-read man.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:44,594" end="00:12:47,409">He really does know a lot of things.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:47,409" end="00:12:50,212">He has studied strongly. Self-educated.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:50,212" end="00:12:54,182">I mean, let's say he started at fourteen,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>at Adolph Cohen's, you know what I mean?</p>
      <p begin="00:12:54,182" end="00:12:59,224">He is completely and utterly<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>probably one of the greatest examples,</p>
