      <p begin="00:13:25,296" end="00:13:27,392">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Mosley came out of jail with all the fascists</span></p>
      <p begin="00:13:27,392" end="00:13:29,620">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and they started putting on their uniforms again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:29,620" end="00:13:31,345">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They are doing exactly the same thing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:31,345" end="00:13:34,012">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There's no way you could deal with themon an intellectual level</span>
