      <p begin="00:13:34,012" end="00:13:36,001">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">or go out and speak your mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:36,001" end="00:13:37,751">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was street fighting.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:37,751" end="00:13:41,885">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And a group of ex-servicemenstarted an anti-fascist group,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:41,885" end="00:13:46,683">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I swear within a year the streets were cleaned of fascists.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:46,683" end="00:13:49,327">- Youngsters like myself, we joined.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:49,327" end="00:13:51,415">And we were given all the information.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:51,415" end="00:13:52,249">Where they would be.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:52,249" end="00:13:53,516">Where they've had their meetings.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:53,516" end="00:13:56,299">We do some damage.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:56,299" end="00:13:58,428">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Announcer] And then the Mosley heist</span></p>
      <p begin="00:13:58,428" end="00:13:59,928">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">moved into Londonto hold a rally in Dalston.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:59,928" end="00:14:02,466">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Scene of many Mosley riotsin pre-war days.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:02,466" end="00:14:08,353">- There was always this sense <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of having to prove something to myself.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:09,769" end="00:14:12,789">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was a very personal thing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:12,789" end="00:14:14,432">[people shouting and fighting]</p>
      <p begin="00:14:14,432" end="00:14:17,282">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Oh, I once came to workbruised on one side.</span>
