      <p begin="00:14:21,211" end="00:14:24,211">"[whisper tone] Good God! <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>What happened to your face?"*</p>
      <p begin="00:14:24,211" end="00:14:28,183">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I said am nothing man, I just tripped over a hip and...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:28,183" end="00:14:31,069">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic">After the Holocaust,you couldn't just sit at home</span></p>
