      <p begin="00:14:34,878" end="00:14:37,878">"We gotta get rid of the Yids."</p>
      <p begin="00:14:37,878" end="00:14:40,041">They already got rid of six million.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:40,041" end="00:14:42,718">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Announcer] In May of 1948, a new Jewish state, Israel,</span></p>
