        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in the first of a series of battlesthat were to reverberate through the years</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:51,696" end="00:14:56,563">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] I found the concept ofgoing to Israel so fascinating.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:14:56,563" end="00:15:02,279">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That I put my name down and spent probablyone of the great years of my life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:02,279" end="00:15:04,469">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I found myself there as a human being.</span>
