      <p begin="00:15:04,469" end="00:15:07,541">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I mean I didn't think of the great tragedy of the war.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:07,541" end="00:15:09,745">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I just thought as a kid it was an adventure.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:09,745" end="00:15:14,544">&#9834; [drumbeat] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:15:14,544" end="00:15:15,730">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It became a state May '48.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:15,730" end="00:15:17,620">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I didn't get there till July.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:17,620" end="00:15:22,509">&#9834; [whistling sound] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:15:22,509" end="00:15:27,975">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
