        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Tough times when comrades were either killed or wounded.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:32,141" end="00:15:35,555">It was a fascinating experience <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>being with those people</p>
      <p begin="00:15:35,555" end="00:15:39,223">and sharing what I shared there.</p>
      <p begin="00:15:41,978" end="00:15:44,451">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Before I went through Israel,I didn't know who I was.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:44,451" end="00:15:47,677">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As a Jew, you are a minority in every European country.</span>
      </p>
